item.title: Bleu x Patch
item.description: This pairing was between our third generation hold back, Patch, and our male from Jeremy Booker, Bleu, from Brightside Chameleons. Bleu is the only male with Stryfe in him and we are excited to see what that brings to the project. Manga was our keeper from this group. Bleu x Patch Hatch dates 9/12/2020 - 9/27/2020 Hatch rate 29/32 F1 F2 F3 F4 M1 M2 Manga7 Hatch dates 10/28/2020 - 11/17/2020 Hatch rate 33/41 F1

item.title: Bleu
item.description: Bleu is a male we picked up from the Stryfe line. He was raised by Jeremy Booker at Brightside Chameleons, and he was a bit of a challenge to work with. We released him in early 2020 and only produced a few clutches with him. We hope to select some nice males from his offspring to bring that line into our project.
